ModuleInfo.Description: Exports an Emme worksheet to a file (e.g. PDF or PNG). The network view can be configured to use the current view (not recommended) or a pre-specified view. Worksheet parameters can also be configured to allow custom meta-data or other information to be set individually per worksheet export.
